  <brief_title>Study of Rubitecan in Cancer Patients With Renal or Hepatic Dysfunction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase I Study of Rubitecan (RFS 2000) in the Treatment of Cancer Patients With Organ Dysfunction</official_title>
  <sponsors>
